    slug: 'health-data-analytics-east-africa-investor-intelligence',
    title: 'Health Data Analytics in East Africa: Monetising the Information Layer Above a Fragmented Healthcare System',
    metaDescription: 'East African healthcare generates vast volumes of unstructured data that remains unanalysed. An investor guide to health data analytics businesses serving payers, providers, and public health agencies.',
    cluster: 'Healthcare — East Africa',
